	* src/shmem/: Makefile.am: %[PR: 150]%

	  The header files of Common/shmem will now be installed in
	  include/Common/shmem.

2005-04-06 17:28  loose

	* src/Net/Socket.cc: %[ER: 231]%

	  Socket::shutdown() no longer closes the socket; this is now done
	  by Socket::close(). Otherwise you would get an error when
	  Socket::~Socket() calls Socket::close() to close an already
	  closed socket.

2005-04-05 10:09  loose

	* src/Net/Socket.cc: %[PR: 148]%

	  Fixed potential bug in Socket::errstr(), where the wrong system
	  error code (errno) could be returned.

