2005-01-13 15:35  romein

	* src/KeyValue.cc: %[ER: 223]% Avoid icc (EM64T) compiler bug.

2005-01-13 08:40  overeem

	* src/Net/Socket.cc: %[ER:30]% Blue Gene does not have sockopt
	  calls, made them dependent from the HAVE_BGL definition.  On
	  read/write errors the socket is not immediately closed anymore
	  allowing the user to get the SocketID from the Socket in trouble.
	  Prevents redundant administration is several cases.

