	  casa namespace

2005-01-06 18:02  loose

	* src/: Makefile.am, shmem/Makefile.am: %[ER: 177]%

	  Shared memory can now be enabled or disabled using
	  --with-shmem=[yes|no] during configure. Furthermore,
	  --with-shmem=yes has been made the default for the standard
	  variant (e.g. debug, opt, mpich, etc.); the bgl and fakebgl
	  variants use --with-shmem=no by default.

