2004-12-01 14:01  loose

	* src/: LofarLog4Cplus.h, LofarLogCout.h, LofarLogger.h: %[ER:
	  119]%

	  Redefined the logger macros so that they now use the full package
	  name LOFARLOGGER_FULLPACKAGE, which is the concatenation of the
	  package name LOFARLOGGER_PACKAGE (as derived by lofarconf) and an
	  optional user-defined sub-package name LOFARLOGGER_SUBPACKAGE.

