2004-11-15 10:47  loose

	* src/Net/Socket.cc: %[ER: 30]%

	  Reverted to the previous version. Throwing an exception was
	  causing too much trouble. Besides, the error reporting facilities
	  were too limiting, because only one type of exception was being
	  thrown, whereas the status code provides a much richer source of
	  information.

